// ─── Controllers ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
// This directory contains route handler functions (controllers).
// Each controller file should handle the business logic for a specific
// resource or feature of the SkillForge API.
//
// Example:
//   authController.js   → login, register, verifyToken
//   courseController.js  → getCourses, createCourse, updateCourse
//   userController.js    → getProfile, updateProfile
